dc_title_s: Bunkyū kaikoku hanʼei Kyōto onʼezu zusho narabini kōtei Yomo Shunsui.
dc_description_s: Mounted cover title. Wood block print. Oriented with north to the left. In Japanese. Relief shown pictorially. Includes legend. Engraved by Nakamura Katsunosuke. 1 map: 50 x 71 cm., folded in cover 18 x 13 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
